snippet: D.C. United scored in the 88th minute to win and advance to the M.L.S. Eastern Conference finals, knocking the Red Bulls out of the playoffs.
abstract: DC United defeats New York Red Bulls, 1-0, to advance to MLS Eastern Conference finals.
lead_paragraph: D.C. United scored in the 88th minute to win and advance to the M.L.S. Eastern Conference finals, knocking the Red Bulls out of the playoffs.

headline.seo: In Wild Finish, Red Bulls Go From Elated to Eliminated
headline.main: In Minutes, Red Bulls Go From Elated to Eliminated
